.Sh NAME
.Nm AG_Text
.Nd agar text rendering interface
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Bd -literal
#include <agar/core.h>
#include <agar/gui.h>
.Ed
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.\" IMAGE(http://libagar.org/widgets/AG_Textbox.png, "The AG_Textbox(3) widget")
The
.Nm
interface enables Agar applications to size and render text.
Currently, two font engines are supported:
.Dv AG_FONT_VECTOR
(using FreeType) and
.Dv AG_FONT_BITMAP
(simple built-in bitmap font renderer).
.Sh RENDER SETTINGS
A number of settings which affect the rendering functions (see
.Sx RENDERING
section) can be modified at any time, and are organized in a stack of
rendering attributes.
